commit.message:
calls.c (emit_library_call_value_1): Fix a comment typo.

2001-07-10  Kazu Hirata  <kazu@hxi.com>

	* calls.c (emit_library_call_value_1): Fix a comment typo.
	* dwarf2out.c (mem_loc_descriptor): Likewise.
	* config/i386/i386.c (ix86_expand_aligntest): Likewise.

From-SVN: r43917
